You can use `MockRestServiceServer` from [Spring Test][1].

This way you can test the expected behaviour without having to run a Server or call the actual exchange method, like so (Example form the docs):

``` 
RestTemplate restTemplate = new RestTemplate();

MockRestServiceServer mockServer = MockRestServiceServer.bindTo(restTemplate).build();
